- **`push(item)`**: This method adds an item to the top of the stack by using the `append()` method of the list.
- **`pop()`**: This method removes and returns the topmost item from the stack. If the stack is empty, it returns `None`.
- **`peek()`**: This method returns the topmost item from the stack without removing it. If the stack is empty, it returns `None`.
- **`size()`**: This method returns the number of items in the stack, which is the length of the list.

